  <body id="msgFeedSummaryBody" selected="false">
    <p>Drupal image fields allow content editors to upload photos and pictures without tedious manual cropping and scaling. One posted, images are piped through a series of automatic cropping and scaling presets, ensuring everything is fast and consistent. Unfortunately, all that automation can be a problem when content creators <em>do</em> need to tweak how an image will appear at different sizes. When that's the case, the <a href="https://drupal.org/project/imagefield_focus">Imagefield Focus</a> module can help.</p>
